HEADWORD: -taxis
<hw>-tax"is</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>combining form for
<er>taxis{3}</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>taxi</ent>⟦br⟧
